WEBVTT

00:00.077 --> 00:01.543
<i>Previously on Monk...</i>

00:01.659 --> 00:04.405
The crime scene boys found something
here that might upset you.

00:04.514 --> 00:06.154
Look at the fingerprints.
Thumb,

00:06.230 --> 00:09.669
index finger, middle finger.
Ring finger, pinky.

00:09.814 --> 00:10.721
Six fingers?

00:10.759 --> 00:13.426
20 years, I've only seen
one other bomb like that.

00:13.484 --> 00:15.424
Trudy?
<i>Trudy!</i>

00:17.807 --> 00:19.753
I said, stay back!
I mean it!

00:19.869 --> 00:21.559
Wait a minute,
i know you.

00:21.633 --> 00:23.817
- You're the cop with the wife.
- Who hired you?

00:23.886 --> 00:25.605
I tell you that, i'm a dead man.

00:28.988 --> 00:32.747
Sheriff's department.
Drop that weapon. I'm not asking twice.

00:32.921 --> 00:35.370
You have the right to remain silent.

00:35.486 --> 00:37.155
You have the right to an attorney.

00:37.208 --> 00:39.725
- What the hell happened?
- Monk jimmied the lock on the van.

00:39.802 --> 00:42.574
He jumped out.
Your boss is a murder suspect.

00:42.594 --> 00:45.657
Right now, he's acting like
a very guilty murder suspect.

00:45.743 --> 00:47.695
If you get a clean shot, bring him down.

00:47.805 --> 00:50.453
Leland, I know who set me up.
It was that sheriff.

00:50.511 --> 00:53.852
- Rollins? Why?
- <i>I don't know why, but I know how.</i>

00:56.064 --> 00:57.264
That was Adrian Monk.

00:57.353 --> 00:59.556
- Call the tac squad.
- He said I should come alone.

00:59.581 --> 01:02.080
- Are you setting me up, Leland?
- Monk, just put the gun away.

01:02.141 --> 01:02.818
Monk!

01:03.866 --> 01:04.599
Monk!

01:05.160 --> 01:06.822
Monk, please, drop the gun!

