40:05.508 --> 40:06.513
Or won't?

40:09.179 --> 40:10.706
A little lead.

40:11.440 --> 40:12.580
How exciting.

40:13.549 --> 40:15.945
That should keep you
off the street for a while.

40:16.499 --> 40:18.995
The important thing
is that you're off the street.

40:19.247 --> 40:21.726
You really think
these bars

40:21.781 --> 40:22.860
can hold me?

40:27.586 --> 40:28.340
Yeah.

40:29.311 --> 40:30.934
They seem pretty strong.

40:32.750 --> 40:34.257
Have a good life, Dale.

40:35.204 --> 40:36.981
It's true, Adrian Monk!

40:37.268 --> 40:40.312
I'm in prison,
but you're in a worse prison!

40:40.436 --> 40:41.538
You're trapped!

40:41.616 --> 40:44.730
Trapped by your own demons!
You're in your own private hell!

40:45.012 --> 40:47.488
I wouldn't trade places with you

40:47.565 --> 40:49.518
for a billion dollars!

40:49.707 --> 40:52.567
I mean, another
billion dollars!

40:53.421 --> 40:54.464
You hear me?

40:54.502 --> 40:57.907
Come back here!
I'm... Not... Done!

40:57.972 --> 40:59.991
Yes, you are.

